---
title: Greek-Style Beef & Spinach Couscous Bowl with Caramelised Onion & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Introduce your tastebuds to the incredible flavour of garlic and herb infused beef; it really packs a punch. Sitting on a hearty bed of couscous and topped with Greek-style yoghurt, this dish offers a depth of flavour that's sure to knock your socks off.
